    owned_media_item (
        owner_id,
        account_id,
        source_id,
        perceptual_hash,
        sha256_hash,
        link,
        title,
        posted_at,
        last_modified
    )

    (
        $1,
        $2,
        $3,
        $4,
        $5,
        $6,
        $7,
        $8,
        current_timestamp
    ) ON CONFLICT (account_id, source_id) DO

SET
    perceptual_hash = EXCLUDED.perceptual_hash,
    sha256_hash = EXCLUDED.sha256_hash,
